Interface Header

  • All Superinterfaces:
    utam.core.framework.base.PageObject, utam.core.framework.base.RootPageObject, utam.core.framework.base.UtamBase

    HeaderImpl
    public interface Header
extends utam.core.framework.base.RootPageObject
    Selector: .oneHeader. Represents the one:header Aura component. Access the system message, global actions list, trailhead trigger, notifications button, notifications count, favorites list, add to favorites button, profile link, setup menu, search, or back button. , created from JSON resources/utam/global/header.utam.json
    Version:
    1.2.0
    Author:
